Gentoo layman overlay for an experemental Apple cross-compiler based on LLVM clang.

Copy metadata/crossdev-apple.xml to /etc/layman/overlays/ to add this repository to layman.
Then install locally via layman -a crossdev-apple && layman -S.

To install:  crossdev -v --target <arch>-apple-darwin<ver>

Ex: crossdev -v --target i586-apple-darwin9
